<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="30Jul1936"><font color="red">30 July 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to John Lane The Bodley Head): Mr Joyce has gone away from Paris for a short time but is still within my reach. By August the 10th he will be however gone away further and it will be difficult for me to reach him. I have been in communication with Mr Young from Bury Street about missprints and so far we have reached I think Page 350 odd of the Albatross text. What about the rest? </div>
